---
import HomeLayout from '../layouts/HomeLayout.astro';

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<HomeLayout>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="shell nav">
      <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="文几 WENJI 首页">文几 WENJI <small>MAKES</small></a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="主要导航">
        <a href="#works">作品</a>
        <a href="#now">正在做</a>
        <a href="#about">关于</a>
        <a href="#links">链接</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
      <div class="shell hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="hero-kicker eyebrow">Stardew Valley Mod Creator</p>
          <h1 id="hero-title">做自己想玩、<span>游戏里没有的内容。</span></h1>
          <p class="hero-intro">我是文几。一个“如果游戏里有这个就好了”的念头，最后应该变成真的玩法，而不是停在脑子里。</p>
          <div class="hero-meta">
            <a href="#works">看我做了什么 <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
            <span class="hero-status">Now making<br />Magic Flute Mod</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <figure class="portrait">
          <div class="portrait-frame">
            <img
              src="/images/home/wenji-avatar.jpg"
              width="1254"
              height="1254"
              alt="文几的角色头像：白绿头发、红色眼眸，衣领写着 E=mc²"
              fetchpriority="high"
            />
            <figcaption class="portrait-caption"><b>Creator identity</b>文几 WENJI · 原创 MOD 创作者</figcaption>
          </div>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="manifesto" id="about" aria-labelledby="manifesto-title">
      <div class="shell manifesto-grid">
        <p class="eyebrow">01 / Why I make</p>
        <h2 id="manifesto-title">我想的是玩法，代码只是把它变成真的方式。</h2>
        <div class="manifesto-copy">
          <p>我从“这个游戏缺什么好玩的”开始，而不是从“我还能加什么功能”开始。</p>
          <p><strong>不做简单的数值修改。</strong>我更在意一个 Mod 能不能改变你进入游戏、安排一天和理解世界的方式。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principles" aria-label="创作特点">
          <div class="principle"><b>01 / IDEA</b><span>从一个真正想玩的念头开始</span></div>
          <div class="principle"><b>02 / SYSTEM</b><span>把它做成完整、能运转的规则</span></div>
          <div class="principle"><b>03 / FEELING</b><span>自己玩起来不够有趣，就不发布</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="works" aria-labelledby="works-title">
      <header class="works-head shell">
        <div class="works-title">
          <p class="eyebrow">02 / Selected works</p>
          <h2 id="works-title">我把这些想法，<br />做成了能玩的东西。</h2>
        </div>
      </header>

      <article class="work">
        <div class="shell work-inner">
          <div class="work-meta">
            <span class="index">01</span>
            <span>Large-scale opening & narrative</span>
            <span class="status">Released / Nexus Mods</span>
          </div>
          <a class="ginger-layout" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/46543" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="在 Nexus Mods 查看 Ginger Island Survival">
            <div class="work-visual" data-fallback="GINGER ISLAND SURVIVAL">
              <img src="/images/home/ginger-island.webp" width="1300" height="372" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="姜岛求生 Mod：玩家在姜岛海岸醒来" />
            </div>
            <div class="work-copy">
              <h3><small>如果开局不是农场呢？</small>Ginger Island<br />Survival</h3>
              <p>因为太想玩姜岛开局，我自己做了个 Mod。你在岸边醒来，一无所有；探索、求生、搭起营地，再一步步挣回大陆。海盗也会在你攒下足够财富后找上门。</p>
              <span class="work-link">进入作品 <span class="arrow">→</span></span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="work">
        <div class="shell work-inner">
          <div class="work-meta">
            <span class="index">02</span>
            <span>Daily rhythm & small system</span>
            <span class="status">Released / Nexus Mods</span>
          </div>
          <a class="fishing-layout" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/47586" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="在 Nexus Mods 查看 Fishing Net">
            <div class="work-visual" data-fallback="FISHING NET">
              <img src="/images/home/fishing-net.webp" width="1300" height="372" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="捕鱼网 Mod：一排渔网布置在海岸水面" />
            </div>
            <div class="work-copy">
              <h3>Fishing<br />Net</h3>
              <p>捕鱼不一定非要一直站在岸边。把渔网放进水里，留它工作一夜，第二天回来收取；耐久度让这套省力的办法依然需要照看。</p>
              <div class="sequence" aria-label="放置、等待、收取">放置 <i></i> 等待 <i></i> 收取</div>
              <span class="work-link">进入作品 <span class="arrow">→</span></span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="work tool-work">
        <div class="shell work-inner">
          <div class="work-meta">
            <span class="index">03</span>
            <span>Power fantasy & spectacle</span>
            <span class="status">Released / Nexus Mods</span>
          </div>
          <a class="tool-layout" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/48087" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="在 Nexus Mods 查看 Universal Tool">
            <div class="work-visual" data-fallback="UNIVERSAL TOOL">
              <img src="/images/home/universal-tool.webp" width="1300" height="372" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="天外陨星尺 Universal Tool 作品横幅" />
            </div>
            <div class="work-copy">
              <span class="tool-tag">故意超模 / Just for fun</span>
              <h3>越来越离谱的<br />星露谷神器。</h3>
              <p>能砸、能砍、能收割、能终结木乃伊，还能召唤旋转剑阵。这里不假装追求平衡——它就是为“爽”做的，包括可以改变天气的「天气之子」。</p>
              <span class="work-link">进入作品 <span class="arrow">→</span></span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="now" id="now" aria-labelledby="now-title">
      <div class="shell now-grid">
        <div class="now-number" aria-hidden="true">06</div>
        <div class="now-copy">
          <p class="eyebrow">Now making / Magic Flute Mod</p>
          <h2 id="now-title">六首曲子，<span>六种能力。</span></h2>
          <p>如果音乐本身就是魔法呢？魔笛 Mod 还在制作中，首版网站只留下这个正在发生的念头。等它正式发布到 Nexus Mods，再把完整的玩法和开发过程补进来。</p>
          <div class="music-lines" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
          <a class="work-link" href="https://xhslink.com/m/7mGN7KQWYMl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">去小红书看开发预告 <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="next" aria-labelledby="next-title">
      <div class="shell next-grid">
        <p class="eyebrow">03 / What comes next</p>
        <div class="next-copy">
          <h2 id="next-title">Mod 不是终点，<br />是我开始做游戏的地方。</h2>
          <p>接下来，我会继续把姜岛求生扩成更大的作品，也会去别的游戏里试新的想法。长远一点，我想做出真正属于自己的游戏。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="future-list" aria-label="未来方向">
          <div class="future-item"><b>NEXT / 01</b><span>姜岛求生大型拓展</span></div>
          <div class="future-item"><b>NEXT / 02</b><span>更多游戏里的 Mod 实验</span></div>
          <div class="future-item"><b>NEXT / 03</b><span>自己的独立游戏</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer" id="links">
    <div class="shell footer-main">
      <h2 class="footer-title">我是文几。<br /><span>作品会继续长大。</span></h2>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="https://xhslink.com/m/7mGN7KQWYMl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">小红书 <span class="arrow">↗</span></a>
        <a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/users/179201778" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nexus Mods <span class="arrow">↗</span></a>
        <a href="https://ko-fi.com/wenjimods" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ko-fi <span class="arrow">↗</span></a>
        <span class="email-pending">专用邮箱准备中</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="shell footer-bottom">
      <span>© {year} 文几 WENJI</span>
      <span>Made for ideas that should exist.</span>
    </div>
  </footer>
</HomeLayout>